channel.title: ScapeRune 513 :)
channel.description:
[img]http://i672.photobucket.com/albums/vv85/Master_Chef/cooltext422182472.gif[/img] This will be a basic description of the server I am working on with RSMedival. This is [b]NOT[/b] an advertisement.
[b]Before you Read[/b] ☑ = Completed ☑ = In progress ☑ = Not started
[b]Server Performance:[/b]
[ul][li]Holds 189 Players (Tested, crashed at 189) ☑[/li] [li]Lag free if you have less then 100 online ☑[/li] [li]Auto-Restart needed? 4 Hours Set. ☑[/li] [li]NPC's affect performance? No. ☑[/li] [li]Crashes? About one every 24 hours. ☑[/li][/ul]
[IMG]http://i672.photobucket.com/albums/vv85/Master_Chef/nolag.png[/img]
[b]Server Features:[/b] [i]What would a server without great features be? Just another piece of shit...[/i]
[ul][li]508 Special Attacks ☑[/li] [li]Dragon Claw Special ☑[/li] [li]Duel Arena ☑[/li] [li]Bounty Hunter ☑[/li] [li]LD/HD Compatability ☑[/li] [li]Recolored Items ☑[/li] [li]Basic 508 Customs (Dragon claws, Dragon plate) ☑[/li] [li]Custom Weapons (With Special Attacks) ☑[/li] [li]Custom Armour (Some operates) ☑[/li] [li]Item Operates (DFS Spec, Anti-Ice Shield, Multi-Cast Staff) ☑[/li] [li]Custom Spells ☑[/li] [li]100% Vengeance ☑[/li] [li]100% God Wars Dungeon ☑[/li] [li]Jad with 63 Waves (3 Waves ATM) ☑[/li] [li]KBD (With magic/melee attack) ☑[/li] [li]Organized areas (Not too crowded) ☑[/li] [li]Working Shops ☑[/li] [li]Trading (So far 95%, we just don't have 'Add X Amount') ☑[/li] [li]Private Messaging (It does not erase after you relog! Saves upon logout now!) ☑[/li] [li]Some reasonable commands (For PKing equiptment) ☑[/li] [li]Every Weapon Special Attack (Also ones for the Customs!) ☑[/li][/ul]
That's about it. Still, better then most 508 servers.
[b]Server Pictures:[/b]
